title: Romeo Tubbs {1950 - Complete Series - Golden Age}
description:
Numbering continues from My Secret Life (Fox, 1949 series) #26 [first issue of Romeo Tubbs was probably meant to be numbered #27, and there was a My Secret Life #27 after the two issues of Romeo Tubbs].

Unusually, the indicia of both issues of this series list "Fox Features Syndicate, Inc.", with a plural "Features". All other confirmed indicia (as of 2011-10-31) are singular
